cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper focuses on improving the performance of convolutional neural networks for image classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of a novel multiple paths convolutional neural network also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the experimentation and analysis of the weaknesses of convolutional neural networks may also fall under the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the paper's focus on image classification may also relate to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
